  - C) Full fine-tune — 5-50+ hours paired data, VITS / StyleTTS2 from scratch.
    Completeness: 10/10 (studio-quality, weeks of training, full prosody control).

Apply this matrix to write `$PLAN_ROOT/{voice-slug}/clone-config.yaml`:

| Tier | Backbone candidates | Data requirement | Training time (single voice) | Quality ceiling |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Zero-shot | XTTSv2, Tortoise, F5-TTS | 6-30s clean reference | None (inference only) | MOS ~3.8-4.2 |
| Few-shot | StyleTTS2 (adaptation head), XTTSv2 fine-tune | 5-30 min paired | 2-8 GPU-hours | MOS ~4.0-4.4 |
